Dear 建富︰

感謝協助，
為進行 AML 紅旗資訊串接，需請你協助確認各功能對應的資料庫 Table，並確認關聯邏輯：

1. 串接邏輯確認：
•	關聯方式：是否所有產品 Table 皆透過 AML_INFO_SEQ 串回 WBS_AML_DETAIL 以取得紅旗（RED_FLAG）資料？
•	異常處理：若該產品 Table 無此欄位（如下表標示「否」者），應透過何種 Key或其他中間 Table 進行關聯 ?

AML_DETAIL_SEQ 欄位結構：
AML_INFO_SEQ, FUN_CODE, ACTION_TYPE, AML_TYPE, CONTENT, COUNTRY_CONTENT, ORDER_NO, IS_UI, FLAG, GOODS_CODE, MERCHANDISE, GOODSCODE_CONTENT
下方為目前參考的 SQL 代碼：
use HKDB
SELECT
 '_' + C.CUSTOMER_ID CUSTOMER_ID,
 A.TRADE_DATE,
 B.FUN_CODE,
 F.FUNC_NAME,
 B.AML_TYPE,
 B.FLAG,
 B.CONTENT,
 D.content as GOODSCODE,
 E.content as MERCHANDISE,
 B.AML_INFO_SEQ

FROM WBS_IMP_LC A
LEFT JOIN (select * from WBS_AML_DETAIL where AML_TYPE = 'RED_FLAG') B ON A.AML_INFO_SEQ = B.AML_INFO_SEQ
LEFT JOIN (select * from WBS_AML_DETAIL where AML_TYPE = 'GOODSCODE') D ON A.AML_INFO_SEQ = D.AML_INFO_SEQ
LEFT JOIN (select * from WBS_AML_DETAIL where AML_TYPE = 'MERCHANDISE') E ON A.AML_INFO_SEQ = E.AML_INFO_SEQ
LEFT JOIN WBS_CIF_CUST_INFO C ON A.CIF_CUST_INFO_SEQ = C.CIF_CUST_INFO_SEQ
JOIN WBS_RAA_FUNC_INFO F ON b.FUN_CODE = f.FUNC_CODE
WHERE
A.TRADE_DATE BETWEEN '20251101' AND '20251130'
AND B.FLAG = 'Y'


